---

<EventLayout
  title="AI Community Journal Club #001"
  date="February 26, 2026"
  location="Belgium"
  type="Journal Club"
  description="A recurring paper-reading evening by AI Belgium and North Star - bringing research out of the lab and into the community."
  images={images}
>
  <p>The first edition of a recurring format co-organized with AI Belgium. A paper-reading evening where researchers and practitioners sit in the same room, discuss the same paper, and bridge the gap between what gets published and what gets built.</p>
  <p>Research doesn't compound if it stays in the lab. These evenings are how we make sure it doesn't.</p>
</EventLayout>
